dev.foxgirl.rembulan.impl

Class AbstractStateContext

  • java.lang.Object
    • dev.foxgirl.rembulan.impl.AbstractStateContext
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MetatableAccessor, MetatableProvider, StateContext, TableFactory

    public abstract class AbstractStateContext
extends Object
implements StateContext
    An abstract implementation of a state context that delegates state context methods to an underlying table factory and metatable accessor.

      • setMetatable

        public Table setMetatable(Object instance,
                          Table table)
        Description copied from interface: MetatableAccessor
        Sets the metatable of the object instance to table. table may be null: in that case, clears instance's metatable. Returns the previous metatable.

        Note that instance may share the metatable with other instances of the same (Lua) type. This method provides a uniform interface for setting the metatables of all types.

        Specified by:
        setMetatable in interface MetatableAccessor
        Parameters:
        instance - object to set the metatable of, may be null
        table - new metatable of instance, may be null
        Returns:
        the previous metatable of instance
